                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010916-98-defend667 t18010916-98-punish512"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
